metadata.name: Archangel # 1
metadata.description:
1080 x 1350 px.

All First Holders will receive a Gaichu OBJ 3d Model & PNG's of their Archangel.
--------
In the year 9000, 7 Bounty Hunters have been sent on a mission to achieve intergalactic peace in the Auraverse. Things go their way, until an unprecedented rip in the spacetime continuum introduces a deadly invasive species set to overtake their realm.

Webcomic Prologue coming Summer 2022 on a free webcomic platform!

First Holders get to choose:

1. The Archangel's Name
2. Nature & Affinity
3. Name of their special attack
4. Archetype
